data.description: Welcome to your dream home in the Lynnwood subdivision of Baytown, TX! This stunning two-story residence boasts 4 bedrooms, 2.5 bathrooms, and a plethora of desirable features. The spacious layout includes a game room and study, providing ample space for work and play. The large yard is a perfect oasis, offering privacy and serenity with no back neighbors. Don't miss this incredible opportunity to make this house your home!
